Dialogs.Dialog: ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Ah...
What's up？ Why did you come here alone？
Well, I was just thinking that I should try reading a book somewhere I don't usually go.
I see. Meeting you unexpectedly like this somehow makes me happy.
...Stop saying embarrassing thing like that.
Why？
No particular reason. I'll go home now.
I see. Then see you.
Okay... See you later.
We meet again. Are you reading a book？
Rinko
Yeah... How about you？
I'm just strolling idly.
I see. Hmm...
I think I'm interrupting your reading time. I'll see you later.
...Okay.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Oh, ▲小早川＊▲. We meet here a lot.
Because it's close to my place. And don't you have anywhere else to go？
This is such a common spot. And it's worth coming because I can see ▲小早川＊▲ here quite often.
You don't have to wait until we meet by chance like this. We can meet any time, you idiot.
Rinko
Eh？ Why！？
Yo, what a coincidence. ▲小早川＊▲, are you here to watch a movie？
Yeah, that's right... How about you？ Are you here by yourself？
Yeah, I'm alone. Huh？ I think ▲小早川＊▲ doesn't like to watch movies though... This is unexpected...
T-That's not the case. This movie is based on my favorite book. That's why...
I see. If you invited me, I could've come with you.
But... The original book is quite extreme... I don't think you'll understand this movie...
I don't mind though.
There are movies that I like to watch alone, okay？ I'm going now.
Rinko
Ah, again！？
▲小早川＊▲. Is there a movie based on your favorite book again？
W-Well, there are many of them lately... ...Bye.
(But the theater she just came out was showing a romantic movie, eh？)
We meet again. You watch movies quiet often, huh？
Rinko
Hmm. Well, occasionally.
What kinds of movies do you watch？
Well, I'm quite into romantic movies. Hehe, is that odd？
Not at all.
Really？ That's good... Okay, I'll get going now.
Rinko
Eh？ Why are you here？
What？ Isn't that ▲小早川＊▲？
Do you come to this place, too？
That's my line. I think you hate exercising.
I hate it... But lately, I think I should start working out.
Are you on a diet？
Hehe, sorry, but I don't think I need to do that.
I just feel like I lack physical strength, especially when I'm playing with my little brother.
Yeah, kids are usually very energetic.
That's why I plan to build some strength. I also aim to improve my kicking power, too.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
We meet again, huh？ Are you still trying to build your strength？ You really work hard.
Yeah, whenever I play with my brother, I'm always the one who gives up first.
I see. Your little brother is very energetic, huh？
Yeah. He looks so cute, but he's really a boy. You should follow his example.
I'll think about that. Bye now.
▲小早川＊▲. You're here again.
Rinko
Yeah, I'm a regular member here already.
I see. It's good to exercise regularly.
Thanks to this place, now I'm having more fun playing with my little brother. Hehe.
(You've really worked hard, ▲小早川＊▲.)
Rinko
Eh？ Are you here to shop？
▲小早川＊▲. What a coincidence？
I've just finished my shopping and am about to go home. And you？ Are you having too much free time and just loafing around？
No. Although I look like this, I'm actually a busy person.
Really？
Yeah, I was busy window shopping...
Also, I was watching people walking around...
Then I was reading some magazines at the bookstore...
Sounds like a very busy schedule. I shouldn't bother you then. I'm leaving.
Okay...
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲. We meet again. You have too much free time, huh？
I'm not that free.
Then tell me. What have you been busy doing today？
What if I say I'm here to be a bodyguard for my girlfriend？
Sounds good enough. Bye.
Sounds good enough, eh！？
Oh, isn't that ▲小早川＊▲？ We meet here a lot.
Rinko
Well, yeah. It's difficult to be a girl, you know？
Oh, difficult, huh...
...Somehow, I feel so annoyed.
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Eh？ What are you doing here？
I should ask you. Do you like this kind of event, ▲小早川＊▲？
It's not really what I like, but I just try various things out.
Um, I see. It's good to try different things while you're still young.
What is that？ You sound like a teacher.
But for such an event with so many people like this, don't you hate it？
Hiya！
Whoa！
Make way. I can't walk.
(That was dangerous...)
Rinko
Ah, you again.
What's with us？ We could've been on a date if we kept running into each other like this.
Well, we don't really have to be on a date. We can chat like this.
Well, that's true.
Going on dates and clinging on to each other. For me, that's not cool.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
I keep running into you here. Do you like this event that much？
That's what I want to ask you, ▲小早川＊▲. I think you don't like this kind of thing.
Why not？ I can change my mind.
Well, if I count how many times we've met here by chance...
The reason I'm here often is because of you！
Rinko
Ah, what a rare chance.
▲小早川＊▲. Are you playing by yourself？
Well, yeah.
Hmm？ You play that fighting game again？
Yeah, I always play this one.
You're very good at it...
Really？ Isn't it natural？
Look at how many people you've beaten.
You wanna try it？ Rinko can play with you.
I think I'll pass.
What！？ You don't want to lose to your girlfriend because you think it's embarrassing, huh？ Isn't that sexism？
(Ah, I lost. The other party has had a winning streak. I can't win.)
Ah！ My opponent！ Isn't that ▲小早川＊▲！？
Rinko
I was thinking that you might see through my movements. You still don't understand you girlfriend.
How could I see it through your gaming habit...？
You still lack of training. There are more for you to study.
I thought it was impossible, but it's really you, huh？
Rinko
Ah！
Playing that fighting game again？
Yeah. Is this bad？ I always enjoy playing games alone. Do you feel bored？
No, you like it like this, don't you？
Yeah. Well... Next time I win a present, I'll give it to you.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲. It's rare for us to meet here.
Are you here to shop？
Well, something like that. You, too？
Yeah. I came here to check out some portable music players.
Hmm？ You want a new one？
Not really. The one I have now is good enough.
I just like to look around this kind of shop for audio and video gadgets. Anyway, I don't know much about them though.
Hmm？ Most girls aren't quite good at something like this though.
Don't put me together with "most girls"！
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Ah...
What？ Why are you staring at those appliances？ Are you trying to train yourself to be a good housewife？
No, I'm not！
Ouch！
I just think that I should help my mom a little bit. Bye.
Rinko
Ah, you're here again.
Don't say it like I'm always hanging around here. By the way, ▲小早川＊▲, what are you doing here？
I have some business here.
I brought some CDs from home to test on the audio players here. Anyway, I don't plan to buy any.
(So, you're just killing some time, then.)
Ah... ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Ah...
What a coincidence. Anyway, I'd say that I'm not surprised anymore to see you here ▲小早川＊▲.
Don't go stereotyping people. Also, stop predicting where we'll run into each other！
Anyway, what's up？ Are you here to buy some CDs？
Well, yeah.
Do you have enough pocket money？
Are you my dad or what！？
Did you brush your teeth today？
Are you my mom or what！？
No matter what happens, you must be strong.
Hey, what are you trying to be this time...？
▲小早川＊▲. You're here again.
Rinko
It's not like I'm always here though.
Are you here to shop？
I'm just looking around. I think it's fun enough that way. Wanna join me？
I'm going home. There isn't anything for me to enjoy here.
Okay, you don't have to enjoy what Rinko likes. Just understand Rinko is enough.
▲小早川＊▲. We meet again. Are you shopping？
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲. I'm just checking out some new songs.
Hmm？ How long have you been here？
Well, about an hour, I guess.
That long？ Don't cause trouble to the store, okay？
You aren't listening to me, huh？
Rinko
Eh...？ Why are you here？
▲小早川＊▲. What a coincidence.
That's my line. Do you like this store？
That's exactly the same thing I want to ask you.
I'm here to buy a present for my little brother... But I really have no idea. I'm not good at this.
The age gap is quite big, but if you have something on your mind, I can help you look for it.
Anything related to "Super Robot Volvavin" would be fine.
All right. Excuse me, I need help here！
I don't think that counts as helping me though.
▲小早川＊▲. Are you looking for something for your brother？
Rinko
Ah, yeah... He wants a different item this time.
You spoiled him.
Urgh... Just this time.
Are you sure？
My brother is just so cute. I can't help it.
Ah, ▲小早川＊▲. Are you here to shop again？
Rinko
How should I say this...？
Why are you always here, all the time？
That's...
Hmm...？
B-Bye now！
Rinko
What are you doing here？
Whoa！ ▲小早川＊▲！？ No, I was just passing by...！
And what is ▲小早川＊▲ doing here！？
There's a maniac record store in this building. So I just visited.
Is that so？ I see...
And, how about you？
Um, my dentist's office is in this building. I'm on my way to visit him.
Huh？ You got cavities？
Yeah, right. And I also come for my regular checkup.
You even took a train to visit a dentist？
Y-Yeah. It has to be this dentist！ Bye now！
Rinko
You're here again...
Oh, ▲小早川＊▲！？
Do you have anything you want to tell Rinko？
T-There's a shortcut here that leads to many places. It's so convenient！
Huh？ So, you're actually just passing by？
Of course！ I have to hurry now.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Whoa！
Can I ask a question？
Sorry, you can't. I'm in a hurry！
Are you running away！？
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲. Are you taking a walk？
Yeah, a little bit.
Oh, I'd better go.
Hmm...
Bye.
Bye-bye.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Yo, ▲小早川＊▲.
I knew it was you when I saw you from afar.
Oh, I'd better go.
Really？
Bye.
See you later.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲. What is it？
Hehe. I saw you from afar.
Oh, I'd better go.
Okay. I know.
Bye.
Bye-bye.
